Title: Adapting the Core Language Engine to French and Spanish  
Author: Manny Rayner and David Carter Pierrette Bouillon 
Address: Suite 23, Millers Yard Cambridge CB2 1RQ United Kingdom  1227 Geneva Switzerland  
